result.name: Gusto Restaurant

reviews.text: Terrible experience.  Dish is not available as seen in front door.  We ordered 2 set meal but 1 is missing.  Lemon is missing in cold lemon tea.  Food is suck.  When we pay the bill, Alipay is out of order!  What a mess!

Actually, I’ve never seen such rude and impolite stuff like the one in this restaurant in my whole life. Even the supervisor was so rude and impolite. 
If you have an eatigo reservation they will treat you like a second class customer in fact which is so insulting. If you want to enjoy your meal I don’t recommend this restaurant as it will ruin your mood. In fact, there’s another customer who was also not happy during his visit and complaining about the ditching of the stuff.

Asian lunch sets were provided at reasonable price.  Environment was country side style.  Opposite to the restaurant was a fast food chain, so their set meals were a bit different from the competitor.  However, table was also shared during rush hours.
reasonable priced food
fair dish. clean environment. not many service waiter.

result.name: Discovery Park

reviews.text: Excellent place for family with kids. Can spend all day here with reasonable cost. Public facilities, shops and entertainment are all well designed with kids in mind. The cinema is even decorated and provided with kids seats and play areas. Coming place is more spacious than you could imagine.
Large mall with wide variety of shops, restaurants, and a cinema, but no supermarket. Great place for families with young kids. Parking is relatively cheap.
Good location, family friendly! Good for shopping with kids

A large and well designed shopping mall. Shops were of large types and properly located at different areas of the mall. Food choices were absurd with a bizarre choice from local fast food to American tastes to top-of-the-class cuisines. A huge recommendation for foodies. Activities there are also never-ending and makes the mall suitable for children and adults of all ages.
Spacious.  Good restaurants.  Convenient supermarket.  Comfortable weeknight visit.

result.name: 嚐味

reviews.text: 我試了這裏的海南雞飯，海南雞未夠滑，醬料應不是正宗的，一般。

不會再去
1.玻璃枱面有水，請中年男侍應抹一抹，抹唔到灘水，連乾既位都濕埋。掉頭走到老遠，問佢攞紙巾抹，即刻串咀: 塊布唔濕點抹枱。 態度極差。
2。點左512鮮茄焗豬扒飯
豬扒梅梅地，只有梳打粉和雪味，無煎香無肉味
飯底又濕又爛，好難食
重點係一片蕃茄都無，個汁係燒汁，不是茄汁真係難食，洋䓤，菠蘿都無，
3。椰子雞湯，有椰子，無椰味，只見豬骨既雞湯
早知去對面大家樂，起碼個汁正常茄汁，有蕃茄有菠蘿。平D仲唔駛俾人串
都是午餐時間來多,上餐時間算是快,食物味道一般.
这里海南雞反也幾好吃.喇沙就一般辣同香味不夠.!!
